    PipeEndpoint

    public static class PipeEndpoint.PipeRequest<I,O>
extends CommunicationMethod<I,O>
    A request method to be executed on a PipeEndpoint. This class can either be used directly by providing functions for input conversion and response processing or it can be subclassed by overriding the methods convertInput(Object) and processResponse(byte[]). In the latter case the functions handed to the constructor should be set to NULL.
